Chu Chu Games Studio Privacy Policy
Privacy Policy
Welcome to ChuChu Games Studio Kids Games! We are committed to ensuring the privacy and safety of our young users. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and disclose personal information in compliance with the Children's Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA).
We respect and value your privacy here at ChuChu Games.
Our Privacy Policy describes the information collected by our company ChuChu Games and our partners, through our mobile applications and the use of the information.
If you have any questions about our privacy policy, please Contact Us.
Apps with Ads
• We do not include third-party advertising in our kids' games designed for children aged 3 and below. Our commitment to providing a safe and child-friendly environment means that there are no ads.
• We do not share data with any third party
• We do not collect any device data for purposes beyond third-party analytics and third-party advertising
• Unity Analytics tracks app install and IAP data mentioned specifically in the App privacy section of the store listing page of each app.
Subscription Services:
Some of our games may offer subscription services for accessing premium content or features. These subscriptions are intended for parental purchase and management. We do not collect personal information from children during the subscription process.
In-App Purchases (IAP):
Our games may offer in-app purchases (IAP) for additional content or features. However, these purchases are designed for parental use only and are not targeted at children. We do not collect any personal information during the in-app purchase process.
Information We Collect:
We do not collect any personal information from children under the age of 13 in our kids' games designed for children aged 3 and below. Our games are specifically crafted to be safe and age-appropriate.
Security:
We take the security of children's information seriously. We implement appropriate technical, administrative, and physical safeguards to protect against unauthorized access, use, or disclosure of personal information.
Changes to this Privacy Policy:
We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting the revised Privacy Policy on our website or within our games. We encourage parents to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any updates.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or suggestions about my Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact me at contact@chuchugames.com
